Sqlite3 (tested with 3.6.10)- http://www.sqlite.org - libsqlite3-dev on debian
LiteSQL (works JUST with 0.3.3) - http://apps.sourceforge.net/trac/litesql/
				  Please correct litesql-0.3.3 sources with this patch, or Dates won't work:
				  http://apps.sourceforge.net/trac/litesql/attachment/ticket/13/litesql-0.3.3-time.patch
				  We do also provide patched LiteSQL 0.3.3 sources

QT (developed with 4.5.0) - http://www.qtsoftware.com/downloads - libqt4-dev on ubuntu

Qmake is also required
